title: NFL Divisional Round Picks, Gambling Weekend Budget (Football 1/11)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Pete Prisco, Nick Kostos and R.J. White to break down the Divisional Round games and make their picks against the spread. The guys continue the bankroll contest for the playoffs and give all their picks for Colts-Chiefs (4:00), Cowboys-Rams (13:15), Chargers-Patriots (26:00) and Eagles-Saints (34:00) plus their exotic picks (42:45).
